Keywords or "reserved" words are lowercase words reserved for Java

ACCESS MODIFIERS
    public  - access given to methods and users of the file
    private - access to the methods of the same file only

???
	new	- creates a new object of the specified class

???
    static - static methods can be called without initializing the object

CONTROL STATEMENTS
    if      - single-selection statement
    else    - after an initial if for a double-selection statement
    switch  - multiple-selection statement
    while   - repeats a block of code zero or more times
    for     - repeats a block of code zero or more times
    do...while - repeats a block of code one or more times

???
    break       - breaks away from a loop or switch statement
    continue    - proceeds to the next iteration of a loop
